buy goods - ship goods - sell goods

ship goods with spaceships
buy spaceships setup tradroutes

goods market, prices fluctuate according to supply and demand
goods can be 'processed' in 'better' goods i.e. carbon into Cabon Fibres

some routes more dangerous and have chances to lose ships
can reduce chance by having fighter escorts

buy spaceports to automate spaceship production
can build fighters, or freighters at space ports
make code to setup routes for automated ships

every system has one good that they produce
every system has on processing facility
